717/******************************************************************************/
718/* Peripheral Registers_Bits_Definition */
719/******************************************************************************/
720
721/******************************************************************************/
722/* */
723/* Analog to Digital Converter */
724/* */
725/******************************************************************************/
726
727/******************** Bit definition for ADC_SR register ********************/
728#define ADC_SR_AWD_Pos (0U)
729#define ADC_SR_AWD_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_AWD_Pos)
730#define ADC_SR_AWD ADC_SR_AWD_Msk
731#define ADC_SR_EOC_Pos (1U)
732#define ADC_SR_EOC_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_EOC_Pos)
733#define ADC_SR_EOC ADC_SR_EOC_Msk
734#define ADC_SR_JEOC_Pos (2U)
735#define ADC_SR_JEOC_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_JEOC_Pos)
736#define ADC_SR_JEOC ADC_SR_JEOC_Msk
737#define ADC_SR_JSTRT_Pos (3U)
738#define ADC_SR_JSTRT_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_JSTRT_Pos)
739#define ADC_SR_JSTRT ADC_SR_JSTRT_Msk
740#define ADC_SR_STRT_Pos (4U)
741#define ADC_SR_STRT_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_STRT_Pos)
742#define ADC_SR_STRT ADC_SR_STRT_Msk
743#define ADC_SR_OVR_Pos (5U)
744#define ADC_SR_OVR_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_OVR_Pos)
745#define ADC_SR_OVR ADC_SR_OVR_Msk
746
747/******************* Bit definition for ADC_CR1 register ********************/
748#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos (0U)
749#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Msk (0x1FUL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
750#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Msk
751#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_0 (0x01UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
752#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_1 (0x02UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
753#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_2 (0x04UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
754#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_3 (0x08UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
755#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_4 (0x10UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
756#define ADC_CR1_EOCIE_Pos (5U)
757#define ADC_CR1_EOCIE_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR1_EOCIE_Pos)
758#define ADC_CR1_EOCIE ADC_CR1_EOCIE_Msk
759#define ADC_CR1_AWDIE_Pos (6U)
760#define ADC_CR1_AWDIE_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR1_AWDIE_Pos)
761#define ADC_CR1_AWDIE ADC_CR1_AWDIE_Msk
